Oct. 26, 1969 D Skelmersdale Contest (Section B)
Skelmersdale Contest (Section B) 20 Own Choice Test Piece Contest Skelmersdale Contest skelmersdale-contest-section-b
Brookfield School, Skelmersdale, Lancashire, England, UK Prizes - 1st £20 and rose bowl, 2nd £12 and cup, 3rd £8 and cup. Best horn - Bedford Church. Best trombone - Delph. Best euphonium - Hathern. Best cornet - Pemberton Old. 11 bands competed. 2nd annual contest.
